esa está ocupada<br>¿Que quieres hacer?                    <div class="w3-margin-top w3-margin-bottom w3-center">                        <button class="w3-btn w3-indigo w3-small" style="width:30%;margin-right: 5px;" id="crear">AÑADIR</button>                        <button class="w3-btn w3-indigo w3-small" style="width:30%;" id="liberar">LIBERAR</button>                        <button class="w3-btn w3-indigo w3-small" style="width:30%;margin-left: 5px;" id="" onclick="document.getElementById('id002').style.display = 'none';">NADA</button>                    </div>                </div>            </div>            <div class='toast' style='display:none'>Mesa liberada</div>    </body></html>